Individual decor can be made with a personal inscription that will remind you of the happy moments of your life! A decorative sign can be hung on the wall. A heart-shaped plaque will perfectly decorate your room, give you comfort and remind you of wonderful moments with your loved one!

The decorative plaque is made of eco-friendly natural wood.
